{"tid":674289,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本港大學普通話破壞力評級排名 2018","createTime":"2018-05-22T14:20:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T12:08:47.000Z","uid":63183,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0df31175b0254a8249357ec0c1d6cb920792b505","tid":674289,"uid":63183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T14:20:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/22/222031_3e07fb6b0a03d4844dad5a80e70cf48a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F22%2F222031_3e07fb6b0a03d4844dad5a80e70cf48a.jpg&h=152d433b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n◤港語學宇宙大學排名 2018 （香港站）普通話破壞力評級◢<br />\n<br />\n聽晚十二點，各位應屆 DSE 同學就冇得再更新 JUPAS 課程選擇喇；原來九間參與院校之中，唔係每一間啲語文政策都係人咁品㗎。惟本會特約調查員偵知，唔少大學啲普通話畢業要求並未公諸入學簡介，萃萃學子隨時學費都交埋先發現自己被監人賴厚！特此為各校推廣普通話措施啲破壞力評一評級，供大家參考。<br />\n<br />\n【災難】浸會大學<br />\n浸會大學有「普通話畢業門檻」，規定所有本科生必須修讀3學分嘅普通話課程，並且通過考試後方可畢業。不過，由於門檻飽受爭議，校方舊年決定推出「豁免試」，合格就可獲豁免。<br />\n<br />\n不過，結果反映浸大出爾反爾，聲稱只考「基本溝通能力」嘅豁免試竟然僅三成人合格，試題被揭發難過國家語委考試。最近校方更用鐵腕手段，即時將抗議學生停學，拒絕佢哋上訴，引嚟全港嘩然。浸大學生公開呼籲，千祈唔好報讀該校，否則四年大學生活只會係折磨。<br />\n<br />\n【嚴重】教育大學、嶺南大學<br />\n你喺中小學已經讀咗九年普通話會話，自然想喺大學學返啲高層次啲嘅嘢。不過，教大、嶺大就唔係咁諗。<br />\n<br />\n教大所有課程要求都要求學生，喺普通話水平測試（PSC）中考獲至少三級乙等水平。如學生入學時能通過教大獨有嘅專上普通話測試（Tertiary Putonghua Test, TPT），就可獲豁免；否則，就要修讀由語文教育中心提供無學分普通話課程。<br />\n<br />\n嶺大學生要讀6個學分「實用中文」課程。其中「聽」與「說」兩方面會以普通話進行。學生最多有兩次重修機會，或者可以考評核試，豁免讀實用中文。<br />\n<br />\n【中等】科技大學、城市大學、理工大學<br />\n科大學生必須修讀3個學分嘅中文傳意課程，個課程其中一個目的係提升普通話聽講能力。因此主要都係用普通話教。<br />\n<br />\n理大學生亦都一樣，要讀3個學分、用普通話授課嘅「中文語文及溝通課程」，作為畢業要求。<br />\n<br />\n城大情況就好啲，佢哋要讀「中國文化－歷史與哲學」，而現時普通話班比例有所下調，仍然佔30%。<br />\n<br />\n有趣嘅係，三間大學學生會都仿效浸大發起公投，爭取緊更多粵語教學嘅空間。相信以佢哋管理層唔會好似浸大咁強硬，會更願意同學生溝通，情況進一步改善。<br />\n<br />\n【安全】香港大學、中文大學、公開大學<br />\n香港大學、中文大學，公開大學都無強逼學生讀普通話嘅規定。學生如有需要，可以自由報讀課程。<br />\n<br />\n快啲 tag 你揀緊科啲 fd 子，或者講低你知道更多關於大學語文政策資訊，幫下呢班猶豫未決嘅 DSE 考生啦。"},{"pid":"18a524d06af362be0b0cf09d105505d6274a46cb","tid":674289,"uid":63183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T14:24:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/photos/a.636947586361970.1073741830.593704294019633/1790208401035877\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhongkonglangstudies%2Fphotos%2Fa.636947586361970.1073741830.593704294019633%2F1790208401035877&d=lZkW6VhE5WN5Wr719NYtiu9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=41f380b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/photos/a.636947586361970.1073741830.593704294019633/1790208401035877</a>"},{"pid":"f74bc813e20454c5788a016c89c0a8998d5558e0","tid":674289,"uid":42796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T14:29:31.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"d393dae89ddd58f3027d7c09552819f84f0c3390","tid":674289,"uid":63183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T14:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2f62dc3bac8bf7cfd534e50a030cb379424996","tid":674289,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T14:54:09.000Z","msg":"有埋中小學就最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n排晒band 1 2 3噉"},{"pid":"385bcb4bc6af1e92dc461bc09e85974180bb38c5","tid":674289,"uid":23701,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T14:56:13.000Z","msg":"中大安全？中大係本科生層面的確係冇乜要學讀普通話，但係係教授同埋研究生仲有外來生就仆得直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n教授越收越多中國人，因為要跑出文數，本地學者越黎越小上位機會，你同啲教授講野都大多要普通話。<br />\n研究生同「外來生」又係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中大都係咁先"},{"pid":"58aaa50f51eb8328d7547e5da9636962f7ce8f62","tid":674289,"uid":63183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:48:54.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"8577dd4ea65d43b09ffa96048f3ec7ddcab09594","tid":674289,"uid":140953,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:50:07.000Z","msg":"OU應該拎依個機會大力推廣廣東話<br />\n反正本身都唔會有中國人/外國人去讀<br />\n不如試下全面用廣東話教學，可能有吸引力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb7eb97415b11adf7a629aae6e6c1926a5124d0","tid":674289,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:53:29.000Z","msg":"Ust 今年開咗廣東話course la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b62bcd463590bfdfb2c850ede58f8807eb31ad6c","tid":674289,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:54:36.000Z","msg":"hku 護理系"},{"pid":"6ed11b17b8492b3c9b560a4af5a2833d4b333917","tid":674289,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"edb7eb97415b11adf7a629aae6e6c1926a5124d0","tid":674289,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:53:29.000Z","msg":"Ust 今年開咗廣東話course la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:55:35.000Z","msg":"同埋可以用中化course 頂 佢地用英文或者廣東話上多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3bac71e671f7f200e8c87cddff42f6965e1f7fb","tid":674289,"uid":123308,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:58:59.000Z","msg":"補充資料 1：<br />\n<br />\n大學教育資助委員會（<span style=\"color: blue;\">教資會</span>）University Grants Committee (<span style=\"color: blue;\">UGC</span>) 旗下有八間大學（<span style=\"color: blue;\">八大</span>）<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/XvYe59\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FXvYe59&h=1f0468e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/VNvPLw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FVNvPLw&h=63a58961&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當中本身<ins>一成立就已經係大學嘅大學</ins>只有 <span style=\"color: blue;\">HKUST 香港科技大學</span>，其餘七大院校論獲得／有「大學」頭銜嘅歷史倒時序如下：<br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n- 1881 年：<ins>官立師範學堂 Government Normal School</ins><br />\n<br />\n- 1939 年：<ins>羅富國師範學院 Northcote Training College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/EvNTGR\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FEvNTGR&h=40e17823&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1951 年：<ins>葛量洪師範學院 Grantham Training College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/ezdGkn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FezdGkn&h=c5fc7c34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1960 年：<ins>柏立基師範學院 Sir Robert Black Training College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/RCcEyv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FRCcEyv&h=12ccbd6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1967 年：三所師範學院易名為<ins>教育學院 Colleges of Education</ins><br />\n<br />\n- 1974 年：<ins>香港工商師範學院 Hong Kong Technical Teachers' College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/VqcZuB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FVqcZuB&h=c0f18adb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1982 年：<ins>語文教育學院 Institute of Language in Education</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/FqDDTv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FFqDDTv&h=dc1fc511&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1994 年：五所師訓學院合併為 <strong><ins>HKIEd 香港教育學院 (The Hong Kong Institute of Education)</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/nMVUzd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FnMVUzd&h=8b7ef130&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2016 年</span></span>：獲頒授自我評審資格，取得大學地位，正名為 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">EdUHK 香港教育大學 (The Education University of Hong Kong)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/vCdavY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FvCdavY&h=ee4a3fd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n- 1888 年：<ins>格致書院</ins>（廣州）<br />\n- 1903 年：<ins>嶺南學堂</ins>（廣州）<br />\n- 1912 年：<ins>嶺南學校</ins>（廣州）<br />\n- <strong><ins>1927-1952 年</ins></strong>：<strong><ins>嶺南大學</ins></strong>（廣州）<br />\n- 1967 年：<ins>嶺南書院 Lingnan College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/zgSkFR\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FzgSkFR&h=cf3d2753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n- 1978 年：<ins>嶺南學院 Lingnan College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/jeNgV4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FjeNgV4&h=2ebe6077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1999 年</span></span>：獲頒授自我評審資格，取得大學地位，正名為 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">LU 嶺南大學 (Lingnan University)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/jyxiWg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FjyxiWg&h=10cb3cf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n- 1937 年：<ins>香港官立高級工業學院</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/XzYfmH\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FXzYfmH&h=15df4cf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1947 年：<ins>香港工業專門學院 Hong Kong Technical College (HKTC)</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/mbJhbW\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FmbJhbW&h=3831d4ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://goo.gl/muYqzQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FmuYqzQ&h=495bba67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1972 年：<ins>香港理工學院 Hong Kong Polytechnic</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/MwMofP\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FMwMofP&h=3e6ef969&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://goo.gl/Z9za5V\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FZ9za5V&h=c7ce1665&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- <spa